metadata.name: You Only Love Me When You Want To Have Fun
metadata.description:
You ascend upon me, in search of my heart, but it was taken long before. How do I endure, you ask? I cannot say, for my heart still beats, just elsewhere. Beware, however, for with every excavation, you inflict pain upon me. I long to love you, but multitudes surround me, and my being is void of affection.

"You Only Love Me When You Want To Have Fun" 2023, Lana Denina
